{"tid":2040234,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《中國日報》公布武漢肺炎起源的重大發現，舉世震驚","createTime":"2020-05-28T12:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T13:05:58.000Z","uid":48040,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b92be1e4474d7bf48da08b7e852a1a8402d072f7","tid":2040234,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"《中國日報》公布武漢肺炎起源的重大發現：<br />\n特朗普說美國1月11號就開始研究疫苗，但中國1月12號先share武漢肺炎基因資料，質疑美國點解可以早一日就掌握病毒資料，相當可疑！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1a5uPgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1a5uPgf.jpg&h=246f6e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/398044601_162758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F398044601_162758&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=32c0a0a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/398044601_162758</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實答案好簡單：中國同美國有時差，中國12號，美國係11號。官媒以為大家冇腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如中國叫全世界都用北京時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n五毛話呢個Channel的follower冇可能過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQunCLp8421g&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=0c2dca7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g</a>"},{"pid":"6ae25c622809418bb23fada3932fc0166f59899b","tid":2040234,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2039830/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2039830/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>攬炒要有覺悟</strong></span></spa